}

<div class="featureBanner">
    <div class="bannerContent">
        <h1>
            <strong>Michael Wight</strong>
        </h1>
        <p> Masters of Science in Computer Science</p>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="aboutContentContainer">
    <div class="aboutContent row" id="aboutBio">
        <div class="col-lg-4 bioImageContainer">
            <img src="~/Content/Images/MWightPortrait.jpg" class="bioImage" alt="MWightPortraitImg" />
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-6">
            <h2>Bio</h2>
            <p>Hello, My names Michael!</p>
            <p>
                I'm a Northern Illinois University graduate from Rockford, Illinois, with a degree in Computer Science and Software Development.
                I pride myself as a goal oriented individual with a strong value in teamwork, collaboration, and dedication.
                I've always loved discovering and understanding the details about how things work and my passion and dedication is what continues to drive me through life.
            </p>
            <p>
                Throughout my years of study I’ve elevated my critical thinking and self-learning abilities so that I’d complete all the tasks given to me.
                In my studies I've gained important experience in relational databases, object oriented programming design, data structure, algorithms, and
                collaboration with classmates to discover web design in a software frameworks class where I worked with ten different popular frameworks.
            </p>
        </div>

    </div>
