                </p>
                <p>
                    &nbsp; Since graduating with my degree I have continued to discover and develop new applications. Some of those include:
                    "Azure Cookbook", "Time Management System -- Meteor", "WebAPI/Winform application".
                    Some of these you'll find @Html.ActionLink("here on this portfolio webpage", "index", "Portfolio", null, new { @class = "aboutMePageLink" }).
